{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-427","title":"指挥作战","sectionId":"chapter-19","sectionTitle":"政治军事知多少","pageStart":2103,"pageEnd":2107,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":13,"duplicateEntryCount":25,"pages":[{"number":2103,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"427 指挥作战"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"}]},{"number":2104,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"deployment [dɪˈplɔɪmənt]","headword":"deployment"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.部署"},{"type":"note","text":"◎deployment diagram部署图"},{"type":"entry","text":"intelligence collection情报收集","headword":"intelligence collection"},{"type":"entry","text":"citadel [ˈsɪtədəl]","headword":"citadel"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.堡垒，要塞"},{"type":"entry","text":"take cover 隐蔽，躲藏","headword":"take cover"}]},{"number":2105,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"mobilise [ˈməʊbəlaɪz]","headword":"mobilise"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.动员；调动；集合"},{"type":"note","text":"◎mobilise the army调动军队"},{"type":"entry","text":"open fire 开火","headword":"open fire"},{"type":"entry","text":"aim at the target 瞄准目标","headword":"aim at the target"},{"type":"entry","text":"under attack 在攻击之下","headword":"under attack"}]},{"number":2106,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"escape [ɪˈskeɪp]","headword":"escape"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./v. 逃跑，逃脱"},{"type":"note","text":"◎escape from逃跑"}]},{"number":2107,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"decode the signal 解码信号","headword":"decode the signal"},{"type":"entry","text":"cease fire 停火","headword":"cease fire"},{"type":"entry","text":"captive [ˈkæptɪv]","headword":"captive"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.被俘虏的；被迷住的"},{"type":"definition","text":"n. 俘虏"},{"type":"entry","text":"prisoner of war 战俘","headword":"prisoner of war"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：We need help, for the enemy's combat power is very strong.（我"},{"type":"text","text":"们需要支援，因为敌军的战斗力十分强劲。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：We will mobilise the reserves immediately. （我们将立即调动后"},{"type":"text","text":"备军。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：What should we do when the enemy opens fire? （当敌军开火的"},{"type":"text","text":"时候我们怎么办？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：We should take cover. （我们要隐蔽。）"}]}]}